{"tid":1398981,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"轉場既手足記得頭也不回啊！","createTime":"2019-08-03T04:09:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T04:47:41.000Z","uid":284778,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"18fd6ea3d6fc21bd19258b26de11b6036a34dbb7","tid":1398981,"uid":284778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T04:09:02.000Z","msg":"發夢上次星期兵分幾路係幾好，我同啲朋友都去左cwb<br />\n又物資鏈又路障搞左一大輪<br />\n但係見到上環比人圍<br />\n又死死地氣行番去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n攰到仆街<br />\n沿途都係見到人行去上環<br />\n結果越黎越多人比人圍<br />\n今日見個勢9成都係個局引我地<br />\n就算我地轉左場 警9都會係旺角落重本 等我地番轉頭支援<br />\n所以be water<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然我覺得一定有人留守旺角 唔番去又好似掉低手足<br />\n好撚爭扎<br />\n但係我地試下拎番個主導權啦 轉場搵番我地既主場踢<br />\n撚死班警9<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1305a416064b0d72ae8293eb100a498d321423a6","tid":1398981,"uid":284778,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T04:11:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"caee88ec73ff4eeaa28335dcbfac89b8487df6bc","tid":1398981,"uid":284778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T04:13:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6341335324eefb6af9bf6d3e44c1c7e9270a8b0d","tid":1398981,"uid":284778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T04:14:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1c545b54dfb0bdebbc1848108d3d74f359408c9e","tid":1398981,"uid":294052,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T04:15:20.000Z","msg":"要救到旺角被困既手足 唯有直取要害高鐵站<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55cd6cb2c05e4eaef00be7b157b417de8b87de15","tid":1398981,"uid":284778,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1c545b54dfb0bdebbc1848108d3d74f359408c9e","tid":1398981,"uid":294052,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T04:1